not spoil his structure.} (7. e3 $6 Bxc3+ 8. bxc3 Nxc5 9. Qc2 O-O 10. Be2 b6
11. Ba3 Ba6 $15 {Markovic,M (2240)-Kosic,D (2481) Sombor 2010 (0-1, 52)}) 7...
