is similar.}) 13... c4 14. Qc2 (14. O-O Nc5 15. Qc2 Nb3 $15) (14. Bxc4 $2 Nb6
15. Qb3 Nxc4 16. Qxc4 Ba6 $19 {The white king will be stuck in the centre.})
14... Bc5 (14... Ba6 $5 15. O-O Nc5 {The most ambitious.}) 15. Na4 Ba7 16. Bxc4
